            "stanza_text": "Tout hier, le soleil a boudé dans ses brumes,\nLe vent jusqu'au matin n'a pas décoléré,\nMais, nous point des coteaux là-bas, un œil sacré\nQui va vous bousculer ces paquets de bitume !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "‒ Ah ! Vous m'avez trop, trop vanné,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Bals de diamants, hanches roses ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Et, bien sûr, je n'étais pas né",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Pour ces choses.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Ah ! Vous m'avez trop, trop vanné,\nBals de diamants, hanches roses ;\nEt, bien sûr, je n'étais pas né\nPour ces choses."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "‒ Le vent jusqu'au matin n'a pas décoléré.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Oh ! Ces quintes de toux d'un chaos bien posthume,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Le vent jusqu'au matin n'a pas décoléré.\nOh ! Ces quintes de toux d'un chaos bien posthume,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "‒ Prés et bois vendus ! Que de gens,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "Qui me tenaient mes gants, serviles,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "À cette heure, de mes argents,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Font des piles !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Prés et bois vendus ! Que de gens,\nQui me tenaient mes gants, serviles,\nÀ cette heure, de mes argents,\nFont des piles !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "‒ Délayant en ciels bas ces paquets de bitume",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Qui grimpaient talonnés de noirs Misérérés !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Délayant en ciels bas ces paquets de bitume\nQui grimpaient talonnés de noirs Misérérés !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "‒ Elles, coudes nus dans les fruits,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Riant, changeant de doigts leurs bagues ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Comme nos plages et nos nuits",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Leur sont vagues !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Elles, coudes nus dans les fruits,\nRiant, changeant de doigts leurs bagues ;\nComme nos plages et nos nuits\nLeur sont vagues !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "‒ Oh ! Ces quintes de toux d'un chaos bien posthume,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Chantons comme Memnon, le soleil a filtré,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Oh ! Ces quintes de toux d'un chaos bien posthume,\nChantons comme Memnon, le soleil a filtré,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "‒ Et moi, je suis dans ce lit cru",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "De chambre d'hôtel, fade chambre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Seul, battu dans les vents bourrus",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "De novembre.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Et moi, je suis dans ce lit cru\nDe chambre d'hôtel, fade chambre,\nSeul, battu dans les vents bourrus\nDe novembre."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "‒ Qui, consolant des vents les noirs Misérérés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Des nuages en fuite éponge au loin l'écume.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Qui, consolant des vents les noirs Misérérés,\nDes nuages en fuite éponge au loin l'écume."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "‒ Berthe aux sages yeux de lilas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Qui priais Dieu que je revinsse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Que fais-tu, mariée là-bas,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "En province ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "3",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Berthe aux sages yeux de lilas,\nQui priais Dieu que je revinsse,\nQue fais-tu, mariée là-bas,\nEn province ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "‒ Memnons, ventriloquons ! Le cher astre a filtré",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Et le voilà qui tout authentique s'exhume !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": ""
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "‒ Memnons, ventriloquons ! Le cher astre a filtré\nEt le voilà qui tout authentique s'exhume !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 12,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "‒ Oh ! Quel vent ! Adieu tout sommeil ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Mon Dieu, que je suis bien malade !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Oh ! Notre croisée au soleil",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": ""
                },
                {
